<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ro">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Feedback Revizie – WinDoors Automatic</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,300;0,9..40,400;0,9..40,500;1,9..40,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{
  --bg:#D0C9BD;
  --surface:#fff;
  --ink:#1A1A1A;
  --muted:#6B6760;
  --accent:#2D5BE3;
  --accent-l:#EEF2FD;
  --border:#C4BDB1;
  --green:#1A7A4A;
  --green-l:#EDFAF3;
  --green-b:#2DBF76;
  --warn:#C84B11;
  --warn-l:#FEF0EA;
  --r:12px;
  --sh:0 2px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.10);
}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--ink);min-height:100vh}

/* HEADER */
.header{
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0D1B2A 0%,#1B2E4B 40%,#1A3A5C 70%,#0F2744 100%);
  color:#fff;padding:32px 32px 40px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;min-height:230px;
}
.hgfx{position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;pointer-events:none}
.header::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:-80px;right:-80px;width:320px;height:320px;border-radius:50%;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(45,91,227,.25) 0%,transparent 70%);animation:drift 8s ease-in-out infinite alternate}
.header::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:-60px;left:30%;width:240px;height:240px;border-radius:50%;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(0,180,160,.15) 0%,transparent 70%);animation:drift 11s ease-in-out infinite alternate-reverse}
@keyframes drift{from{transform:translate(0,0)}to{transform:translate(20px,-20px)}}
.h-company{position:relative;z-index:2;font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,.92);margin-bottom:22px}
.h-tag{position:relative;z-index:2;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.38);margin-bottom:10px}
.header h1{position:relative;z-index:2;font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(22px,5vw,34px);font-weight:800;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:12px}
.header p{position:relative;z-index:2;font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.55);line-height:1.7;max-width:480px}
.h-meta{position:relative;z-index:2;display:flex;gap:20px;margin-top:20px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.h-pill{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.38)}

/* PROGRESS */
.pbar{background:#B8B0A4;height:7px;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100}
.pfill{height:100%;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--green),var(--green-b));width:0%;transition:width .4s ease}

/* MAIN */
.main{max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;padding:28px 20px 80px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px}

/* INTRO CARD */
.intro-card{background:var(--surface);border-radius:var(--r);border:1px solid var(--border);box-shadow:var(--sh);padding:24px;opacity:0;transform:translateY(12px);animation:fadeUp .4s ease .05s forwards}
.intro-card h3{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:16px;color:var(--ink)}
.intro-fields{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px}
@media(min-width:480px){.intro-fields{flex-direction:row}}
.field-wrap{flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px}
.field-label{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);font-weight:500}

/* CATEGORY */
.cat{background:var(--surface);border-radius:var(--r);border:1px solid var(--border);box-shadow:var(--sh);overflow:hidden;opacity:0;transform:translateY(12px);animation:fadeUp .4s ease forwards}
.cat:nth-child(2){animation-delay:.08s}.cat:nth-child(3){animation-delay:.12s}.cat:nth-child(4){animation-delay:.16s}
.cat:nth-child(5){animation-delay:.20s}.cat:nth-child(6){animation-delay:.24s}.cat:nth-child(7){animation-delay:.28s}.cat:nth-child(8){animation-delay:.32s}
@keyframes fadeUp{to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}

.cat-hd{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;padding:16px 22px;border-bottom:1px solid transparent;transition:border-color .2s}
.cat.active .cat-hd{border-bottom-color:var(--border)}
.cat-num{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1.5px;color:var(--accent);background:var(--accent-l);padding:3px 7px;border-radius:4px;white-space:nowrap}
.cat-title{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;flex:1}
.cat-st{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);white-space:nowrap}
.cat-st.done{color:var(--green);font-weight:600}

.cat-body{display:none;padding:22px 22px 26px;flex-direction:column}
.cat.active .cat-body{display:flex}

/* QUESTION */
.qw{display:none;flex-direction:column;gap:11px;animation:fadeUp .25s ease}
.qw.visible{display:flex}
.ql{font-size:14px;font-weight:500;line-height:1.5}
.ql .req{color:var(--warn);margin-left:3px}

/* NAV */
.qnav{display:flex;justify-content:flex-end;gap:8px;margin-top:6px}
.btn-n,.btn-p{padding:9px 18px;border-radius:8px;border:none;font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s}
.btn-n{background:var(--accent);color:#fff}.btn-n:hover{background:#1E47CC}
.btn-p{background:transparent;color:var(--muted);border:1.5px solid var(--border)}.btn-p:hover{border-color:var(--muted);color:var(--ink)}

/* STARS */
.stars{display:flex;flex-direction:row-reverse;justify-content:flex-end;gap:3px}
.stars input{display:none}
.stars label{font-size:28px;cursor:pointer;color:#D4CFC8;transition:color .15s,transform .15s;line-height:1}
.stars label:hover,.stars label:hover~label,.stars input:checked~label{color:#F5A623}
.stars input:checked+label{color:#F5A623;transform:scale(1.15)}
.star-hint{font-size:11px;color:var(--muted)}

/* OPTIONS */
.opts{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:7px}
.opt{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:11px;padding:10px 13px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;cursor:pointer;transition:border-color .15s,background .15s;font-size:14px}
.opt:hover{border-color:var(--accent);background:var(--accent-l)}
.opt input{display:none}
.rdot{width:17px;height:17px;border-radius:50%;border:2px solid var(--border);flex-shrink:0;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;transition:all .15s}
.opt.sel{border-color:var(--accent);background:var(--accent-l)}
.opt.sel .rdot{border-color:var(--accent);background:var(--accent)}
.opt.sel .rdot::after{content:'';width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:#fff}

/* SCALE */
.scale{display:flex;gap:7px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.sb{width:46px;height:46px;border-radius:8px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);background:#fff;font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;color:var(--muted)}
.sb:hover{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent)}
.sb.active{background:var(--accent);border-color:var(--accent);color:#fff}
.slabels{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:3px}

/* NPS */
.nps{display:flex;gap:5px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.nb{width:42px;height:42px;border-radius:8px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);background:#fff;font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;color:var(--muted)}
.nb:hover{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent)}
.nb.active{background:var(--accent);border-color:var(--accent);color:#fff}

/* FOLLOWUP */
.fup{display:none;padding:13px 15px;background:var(--warn-l);border:1px solid #F5C5A8;border-radius:8px}
.fup.on{display:block}
.fup p{font-size:13px;color:var(--warn);font-weight:500;margin-bottom:9px;line-height:1.5}

/* INPUTS */
.ti,.ta{width:100%;padding:10px 12px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:8px;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:var(--ink);background:#fff;transition:border-color .15s;outline:none}
.ti:focus,.ta:focus{border-color:var(--accent)}
.ta{min-height:80px;resize:vertical;line-height:1.6}

/* DIVIDER */
.qdiv{border:none;border-top:1px solid var(--border);margin:20px 0}

/* GOOGLE */
.gsec{background:var(--surface);border-radius:var(--r);border:1px solid var(--border);padding:26px;box-shadow:var(--sh);text-align:center;opacity:0;transform:translateY(12px);animation:fadeUp .4s ease .34s forwards}
.gsec h3{font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px}
.gsec p{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:16px;line-height:1.6;max-width:400px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto}
.gbtn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;background:#4285F4;color:#fff;padding:12px 24px;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;transition:background .15s,transform .15s}
.gbtn:hover{background:#3367D6;transform:translateY(-1px)}

/* SUBMIT */
.subb{opacity:0;transform:translateY(12px);animation:fadeUp .4s ease .38s forwards}
.sub-btn{width:100%;padding:17px;background:var(--ink);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:var(--r);font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;transition:background .2s,transform .15s}
.sub-btn:hover{background:var(--accent);transform:translateY(-1px)}
.sub-note{text-align:center;font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:9px}

/* ═══ CLOSING PAGE ═══ */
.closing{display:none;min-height:100vh;flex-direction:column}
.closing.on{display:flex}

.cl-header{
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0D1B2A 0%,#1B2E4B 40%,#1A3A5C 70%,#0F2744 100%);
  padding:32px 32px 40px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;
}
.cl-header-inner{max-width:680px;margin:0 auto;position:relative;z-index:2}
.cl-header .h-company{margin-bottom:0}

.cl-body{
  flex:1;
  background:var(--bg);
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:center;
  padding:60px 20px;
}
.cl-card{
  background:var(--surface);
  border-radius:20px;
  border:1px solid var(--border);
  box-shadow:0 8px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.12);
  max-width:560px;
  width:100%;
  padding:48px 40px;
  text-align:center;
  animation:fadeUp .5s ease;
}
.cl-check{
  width:64px;height:64px;
  background:var(--green-l);
  border-radius:50%;
  display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  margin:0 auto 28px;
  border:2px solid rgba(26,122,74,.2);
}
.cl-check svg{width:28px;height:28px;stroke:var(--green);stroke-width:2.5;fill:none;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round}
.cl-card h2{
  font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;
  font-size:clamp(20px,4vw,26px);
  font-weight:800;
  color:var(--ink);
  margin-bottom:16px;
  line-height:1.2;
}
.cl-card p{
  font-size:14px;
  color:var(--muted);
  line-height:1.8;
  margin-bottom:8px;
}
.cl-divider{width:40px;height:3px;background:var(--green);border-radius:2px;margin:24px auto}
.cl-contacts{display:flex;gap:12px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:24px}
.cl-contact-btn{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
  padding:12px 22px;border-radius:10px;
  border:2px solid var(--border);
  font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;
  color:var(--ink);text-decoration:none;
  background:#fff;
  transition:all .15s;
}
.cl-contact-btn:hover{border-color:var(--green);color:var(--green);transform:translateY(-1px)}
.cl-contact-btn.primary{background:var(--green);color:#fff;border-color:var(--green)}
.cl-contact-btn.primary:hover{background:#15693E;color:#fff}
.cl-footer{
  text-align:center;
  padding:20px;
  font-size:12px;
  color:var(--muted);
  background:var(--bg);
}

@media(max-width:480px){
  .cl-card{padding:32px 22px}
  .cat-body{padding:16px 15px 20px}
  .sb{width:40px;height:40px;font-size:13px}
  .nb{width:36px;height:36px;font-size:12px}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ═══════════════ FORM PAGE ═══════════════ -->
<div id="formPage">

<div class="header">
  <svg class="hgfx" viewBox="0 0 800 240" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true">
    <line x1="0" y1="60" x2="800" y2="60" stroke="white" stroke-opacity="0.04" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="0" y1="130" x2="800" y2="130" stroke="white" stroke-opacity="0.04" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="0" y1="200" x2="800" y2="200" stroke="white" stroke-opacity="0.04" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="160" y1="0" x2="160" y2="240" stroke="white" stroke-opacity="0.03" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="320" y1="0" x2="320" y2="240" stroke="white" stroke-opacity="0.03" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="480" y1="0" x2="480" y2="240" stroke="white" stroke-opacity="0.03" stroke-width="1"/>
    <line x1="640" y1="0" x2="640" y2="240" stroke="white" stroke-opacity="0.03" stroke-width="1"/>
    <circle cx="690" cy="45" r="95" fill="none" stroke="#2D5BE3" stroke-opacity="0.13" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    <circle cx="690" cy="45" r="58" fill="none" stroke="#2D5BE3" stroke-opacity="0.08" stroke-width="1"/>
    <circle cx="690" cy="45" r="24" fill="#2D5BE3" fill-opacity="0.07"/>
    <polygon points="570,200 635,100 700,200" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-opacity="0.05" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    <line x1="400" y1="0" x2="760" y2="240" stroke="#00B4A0" stroke-opacity="0.07" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    <circle cx="320" cy="80" r="2.5" fill="#00B4A0" fill-opacity="0.28"/>
    <circle cx="480" cy="185" r="2" fill="#2D5BE3" fill-opacity="0.32"/>
  </svg>
  <div class="h-company">WinDoors Automatic</div>
  <div class="h-tag">Servicii de mentenanță</div>
  <h1>Cum a decurs revizia?</h1>
  <p>Mulțumim că ați ales serviciile noastre. Feedback-ul dvs. ne ajută să menținem standardele echipei și să îmbunătățim experiența fiecărui client. Vă rugăm să răspundeți sincer — toate răspunsurile sunt confidențiale.</p>
  <div class="h-meta">
    <div class="h-pill"><span>⏱</span> 5–7 minute</div>
    <div class="h-pill"><span>🔒</span> Confidențial</div>
    <div class="h-pill"><span>📋</span> 7 secțiuni</div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="pbar"><div class="pfill" id="pfill"></div></div>

<div class="main" id="formMain">

  <!-- INTRO -->
  <div class="intro-card">
    <h3>Informații opționale</h3>
    <div class="intro-fields">
      <div class="field-wrap">
        <div class="field-label">Email (opțional)</div>
        <input type="email" class="ti" id="f-email" placeholder="adresa@email.ro">
      </div>
      <div class="field-wrap">
        <div class="field-label">Locație / Obiectiv (opțional)</div>
        <input type="text" class="ti" id="f-location" placeholder="Ex: Str. Exemplu 12, București">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ══ CAT 1: Programare & Sosire ══ -->
  <div class="cat active" id="cat-1">
    <div class="cat-hd">
      <div class="cat-num">01</div>
      <div class="cat-title">Programare & Sosire</div>
      <div class="cat-st" id="st-1"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="cat-body">

      <div class="qw visible" id="q-1-1">
        <div class="ql">1.1. Cât de ușor a fost să programați revizia / intervenția?<span class="req">*</span></div>
        <div class="stars" id="sq11">
          <input type="radio" name="q11" id="q11-5" value="5"><label for="q11-5">★</label>
          <input type="radio" name="q11" id="q11-4" value="4"><label for="q11-4">★</label>
          <input type="radio" name="q11" id="q11-3" value="3"><label for="q11-3">★</label>
          <input type="radio" name="q11" id="q11-2" value="2"><label for="q11-2">★</label>
          <input type="radio" name="q11" id="q11-1" value="1"><label for="q11-1">★</label>
        </div>
        <div class="star-hint">1 = Foarte dificil &nbsp;·&nbsp; 5 = Foarte ușor</div>
        <div class="qnav"><button class="btn-n" onclick="goNext(1,1)">Următoarea →</button></div>
      </div>

      <div class="qw" id="q-1-2">
        <div class="ql">1.2. Echipa tehnică s-a prezentat la lucrare la ora stabilită inițial?<span class="req">*</span></div>
        <div class="opts">
          <label class="opt"><input type="radio" name="q12" value="Da"><span class="rdot"></span>Da</label>
          <label class="opt"><input type="radio" name="q12" value="Întârziere mică (sub 15 min)"><span class="rdot"></span>Întârziere mică (sub 15 min)</label>
          <label class="opt"><input type="radio" name="q12" value="Întârziere semnificativă (15–60 min)"><span class="rdot"></span>Întârziere semnificativă (15–60 min)</label>
          <label class="opt"><input type="radio" name="q12" value="Întârziere majoră (peste 60 min)"><span class="rdot"></span>Întârziere majoră (peste 60 min)</label>
          <label class="opt"><input type="radio" name="q12" value="Nu au sosit / reprogramat fără preaviz"><span class="rdot"></span>Nu au sosit / reprogramat fără preaviz</label>
        </div>
        <div class="qnav">
          <button class="btn-p" onclick="goPrev(1,2)">← Înapoi</button>
          <button class="btn-n" onclick="goNext(1,2)">Următoarea →</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="qw" id="q-1-3">
        <div class="ql">1.3. Ați fost anunțat în avans în cazul unei întârzieri?</div>
        <div class="opts">
          <label class="opt"><input type="radio" name="q13" value="Da"><span class="rdot"></span>Da</label>
          <label class="opt"><input type="radio" name="q13" value="Nu"><span class="rdot"></span>Nu</label>
          <label class="opt"><input type="radio" name="q13" value="Nu a fost cazul"><span class="rdot"></span>Nu a fost cazul</label>
        </div>
        <div class="qnav">
          <button class="btn-p" onclick="goPrev(1,3)">← Înapoi</button>
          <button class="btn-n" onclick="finishCat(1)">Finalizează secțiunea ✓</button>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ══ CAT 2: Eficiență & Siguranță ══ -->
  <div class="cat" id="cat-2">
    <div class="cat-hd">
      <div class="cat-num">02</div>
      <div class="cat-title">Eficiență & Siguranță</div>
      <div class="cat-st" id="st-2"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="cat-body">

      <div class="qw visible" id="q-2-1">
        <div class="ql">2.1. Durata lucrării a corespuns cu estimarea comunicată inițial?<span class="req">*</span></div>
        <div class="opts">
          <label class="opt"><input type="radio" name="q21" value="Da, conform estimării"><span class="rdot"></span>Da, conform estimării</label>
          <label class="opt"><input type="radio" name="q21" value="Mai scurtă decât estimat"><span class="rdot"></span>Mai scurtă decât estimat</label>
          <label class="opt"><input type="radio" name="q21" value="Ușor mai lungă, cu explicație"><span class="rdot"></span>Ușor mai lungă, cu explicație clară</label>
          <label class="opt"><input type="radio" name="q21" value="Semnificativ mai lungă, fără explicație"><span class="rdot"></span>Semnificativ mai lungă, fără explicație</label>
        </div>
        <div class="qnav"><button class="btn-n" onclick="goNext(2,1)">Următoarea →</button></div>
      </div>

      <div class="qw" id="q-2-2">
        <div class="ql">2.2. Echipa a lucrat organizat și eficient pe parcursul lucrării?<span class="req">*</span></div>
        <div class="scale">
          <button type="button" class="sb" data-q="q22" data-val="1">1</button>
          <button type="button" class="sb" data-q="q22" data-val="2">2</button>
          <button type="button" class="sb" data-q="q22" data-val="3">3</button>
          <button type="button" class="sb" data-q="q22" data-val="4">4</button>
          <button type="button" class="sb" data-q="q22" data-val="5">5</button>
        </div>
        <div class="slabels"><span>Deloc organizat</span><span>Complet eficient</span></div>
        <div class="qnav">
          <button class="btn-p" onclick="goPrev(2,2)">← Înapoi</button>
          <button class="btn-n" onclick="goNext(2,2)">Următoarea →</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="qw" id="q-2-3">
        <div class="ql">2.3. Echipa tehnică a respectat normele de protecția muncii și a minimizat expunerea la risc?<span class="req">*</span></div>
        <div class="opts">
